Products.SmallFormatDescription: Streets Cornetto Mini Vanilla With Hazelnuts
Products.FullDescription: Streets Cornetto Mini Vanilla With Hazelnuts
Products.RichDescription:
CORNETTO ICE CONFECTION CLASSIC VANILLA 480 ML
Say goodbye serious and hello joy! This is where we at Streets kiss goodbye to everything serious and put a 'mini' ice cream smile on your face. Streets Cornetto Mini Classic Vanilla is a delicious crispy wafer cone with classic vanilla ice cream, hazelnut topping and don't forget the chocolate tip. Our tasty minis are available in a convenient multipack with 8 mini delights! A frozen dessert to share and enjoy with friends and family, or simply treat yourself! The perfect snack all year around, only Cornetto can satisfy your craving! Between World War 1 and World War 2, Edwin (‘Ted’) Street, thanks to his wife and brother, laid the foundations (in Corrimal, NSW) for what would ultimately become Australia’s biggest and best-known ice cream manufacturer. Streets ice cream was originally made in the back shed by Ted Street. He would then sell these to neighbours along with sweets, cakes and lemonade. Popularity grew, and he soon used a cart, then a one horse power motorbike to sell Streets ice cream. It continued to grow and today Streets ice cream is sold throughout Australia and New Zealand with well-known brands such as Magnum, Paddle Pop, Cornetto, Gaytime, Calippo and Blue Ribbon. Choose Happier Together.
Streets Cornetto Mini Vanilla a delicious cone with a chocolate tip.
Classic vanilla with a hazelnut topping, delivering on a wafer delight!
A convenient multipack with 8 mini cones, that is great to share with family and friends!
A tasty frozen dessert or just a sneaky snack!
Crispy wafer cone for a delicious treat!
Find your convenient family treat in the freezer aisle today.
